{"type":"text","timestamp":1775894949854,"sessionID":"ses_2846ab367ffe9B2Pi8sQHFgXKI","part":{"id":"prt_d7b966c7b001ULrsNS0xIHxKbq","messageID":"msg_d7b96567a001Y7NdJNc8tq6mIt","sessionID":"ses_2846ab367ffe9B2Pi8sQHFgXKI","type":"text","text":"Created proposal.md for Python SDK/CLI testing (AR-040) covering:\n- Test modules: unit, integration, functional, edge cases\n- Coverage targets ≥85% for main client classes\n- pytest framework with HTTP mocking\n- 6-week implementation plan\n- Impact analysis and alternatives\n- Success criteria and resource requirements","time":{"start":1775894949853,"end":1775894949853}}}
